    "Second, student's academic success indicates that they are more likely to succeed in future professions.",
    "Moreover, students who perform well academically may be eligible for scholarships, internships, and employment offers, among other options RastrolloGuerrero et al (2020); Alturki et al (2022).",
    "For instructors, the predictions will help administrators and instructors to identify students who are struggling to complete their course/semester and allow for intervention as soon as possible to provide the necessary support to improve their outcomes and increase the likelihood of success.",
